    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">Last updated: June 15, 2025</p>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">By accessing or using the Convert KSH website ("Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you disagree with any part of these Terms, you may not access the Service.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
