        <p class="mb-4">Convert KSH provides currency conversion tools and related financial information. The information provided on this website is for general informational purposes only and should not be considered financial advice.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">When using our Service, you agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
          <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
          <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
          <li>Not engage in any activity that disrupts or interferes with our Service</li>
          <li>Not attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or networks</li>
        </ul>
